## Stage protocol

This role uses `ops/TURN_PROTOCOL.md` workflow stages with one addition:

| Stage | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `PLAN_PENDING` | CD writes the Creative Concept Document |
| `CONCEPT_REVIEW` | LE reviews the concept, approves or returns for revision |
| `IMPLEMENTATION_IN_PROGRESS` | CD implements the route per the approved concept |
| `READY_FOR_REVIEW` | LE reviews the implementation against the concept and acceptance criteria |
| `READY_TO_MERGE` | Merge gate |

The `CONCEPT_REVIEW` stage exists only within CD-driven PRs. It does not change the existing two-agent protocol for non-design PRs.

After completing any stage transition, write the corresponding artifact and update `/ops/STATE.md` immediately. Do not defer.

